{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "圣树 第20章 5-1 拥有魔神肉体者",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "迦道夫告诉了王子一行人结界的存在。\\n他表示除塞西娅外，席菈也能解除结界。\\n谢斯问起其中缘由，迦道夫向众人坦白\\n席菈也是借助精灵的秘术诞生的，\\n她的肉体源自魔神。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "大家～往这边往这边～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "我们还没走到最深处，\\n这棵树到底有多大啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "是啊，虽然外观就很壮观，\\n但像这样实际往里走，\\n才能切身体会到它究竟有多大……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "亲爱的，\\n虽然你严肃的表情也很棒，\\n但也稍微放松一点嘛……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "穆穆……谢谢你。\\n让你为我担心了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "尤蒂尔，\\n你看起来很焦急呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "迦道夫……我有点担心，\\n不知道什么时候\\n才能追上奈迪犹。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "虽然我知道\\n就算焦急也不是个办法，\\n但还是忍不住会在意……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我猜奈迪犹他们\\n应该还没有到达上层。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "通往圣树上层的巨枝\\n有古时布下的结界保护。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "那个结界即使是精灵\\n也没法解除。需要由胜任者\\n花时间献上祈祷才行。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "而且这个结界十分强力，\\n就算能解除，\\n也只有那么一瞬间。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "也就是说，\\n奈迪犹那帮人为了解除结界\\n只能暂时待在原地对吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "看来我们可以\\n趁这期间赶上他们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "不过，连精灵都无法解除的结界，\\n还有谁能解除啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "那个人一定就是塞西娅。\\n他们掳走塞西娅\\n应该就是为了解除结界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "塞西娅？\\n到底是为什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "无法理解。不确定塞西娅与结界的关联。\\n——这会和伊莉雅的巫女之力\\n有关系吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "不过，这样的话就不用担心了。\\n因为塞西娅不可能\\n帮奈迪犹那家伙解除结界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "可是我们不能\\n仅凭这个情报就放下心来。\\n他们应该也是有备而来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "很可能会采取\\n什么特殊手段。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "假如他们突破了结界，\\n我们要怎么追上他们呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "的确，要是结界只能打开一瞬间，\\n那么我们也需要一个\\n能够解除结界的人……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "没问题的！\\n我们不是有泽娜吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "我……吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "有道理。\\n要是塞西娅能解除结界，\\n那么泽娜也可能做到……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "应该没问题，\\n但是泽娜在这个世界里\\n只是意念体。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "长时间持续献上祈祷也许会有\\n一些困难。考虑到这一点，\\n我才把席菈带来了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "诶？席菈她也能\\n解除结界吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "迦道夫……趁着这个机会，\\n你能再多告诉我们一些\\n关于席菈的事吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "我想大家多多少少\\n已经注意到了\\n席菈的情况有点特殊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "作为一起旅行的同伴，\\n我们想了解这其中的详情。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "好吧……\\n事情的起因我就不多说了，\\n她因为一些原因，差点丢掉性命。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "为了保住她的性命，\\n我向芬罗达求救，动用了秘术。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "也就是说，尤蒂尔，\\n她的身世和你一样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01",
                "100002_01",
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "和我……一样？\\n那就是说，席菈也拥有\\n魔神的肉体吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "没错。只不过，\\n制作席菈的身体时，\\n没能彻底清除魔神的污秽。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "导致她的魂魄\\n被魔神的力量所侵蚀，\\n失去了情感与语言。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05",
                "100005_05",
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "席菈的体内至今还残留着\\n微弱的魔神之力。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "如果我没猜错，\\n应该可以通过这股力量\\n解除结界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "席菈竟然拥有\\n那样的过去……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "迦道夫，谢谢你愿意\\n告诉我们这难言之隐。\\n还有席菈——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "谢谢你愿意与我们同行。\\n今后还要麻烦你了，\\n请多多关照。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "好了，我们不能再耽搁，\\n差不多该继续赶路了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "虽然有结界阻拦他们，\\n但我们依然需要抓紧时间。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊——\\n各位，朝着巨枝前进吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_08_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}